title: Bug 4121: JarExporter causes out of Sync (1GILQD5)
description: Bug 4121: JarExporter causes out of Sync (1GILQD5)
OB: When the exported jar file is overwritten in the same directory (project), an out of sync message is displayed.
EB: The exported jar file should not include itself to avoid the out of sync message.
SR:
To reproduce the issue:
1. Export a directory (project).
2. Place the exported jar in the same directory (project).
3. Overwrite the exported jar file.
4. Observe the out of sync message.
